Rating: 4
I have made this recipe numerous times since it first appeared in 1996. It is delicious and a nice twist on cooked carrots. As did another reviewer, I too halved the amount of water with good results.

Rating: 3
I used half the amount of water. The combination of carrots, cumin, cilantro and hot pepper is a great one. Sort of like parsleyed carrots for North Africa. Unfortunately my group of adult eaters found that the amount of cayenne was a little overpowering. I plan to make this again but only with reduced amounts of cumin and of cayenne.

